A '''G-seat''' is an exact replica of an ejection seat in a jet fighter, but equipped with additional systems that provide [[Haptic communication|haptic]] feedback to the pilot in the seat. This seat is not used on actual aircraft, but rather in [[flight simulators]], especially those without a [[motion platform]], like simulators of jet fighters and helicopters.

